- [ ] SSE endpoint supports `Last-Event-ID` for resume after reconnect
- [ ] SSE endpoint sends `complete` event when build finishes
- [ ] SSE endpoint requires authentication via session check
- [ ] Full log uploaded to S3 after build completes
- [ ] `build_log_s3_key` updated on the deployment record
- [ ] In-memory log buffer cleared after S3 upload

