## Output

After this step:

- `packages/core/src/build/log-broadcaster.ts` provides an in-memory pub/sub for build log events.
- `packages/core/src/build/builder.ts` emits all build output through the broadcaster.
- `apps/dashboard/src/app/api/.../logs/stream/route.ts` streams build logs via SSE.
- Build logs are persisted to S3 after completion for later retrieval (Step 4).
